{"tid":315129,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老母話要同老豆離婚……","createTime":"2017-07-09T18:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T03:52:26.000Z","uid":35248,"like":12,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d2ff18d2c30c1a52d241e3a9d06fb971759283","tid":315129,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:41:21.000Z","msg":"有啲長，件事要由我細個開始講起&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n好細個嗰陣，老母已經成日趁我睏着同老豆鬧交，有時太嘈重會畀佢哋嘈醒，嗰陣剩係識驚同匿喺被竇入面，唔明點解佢哋要鬧交<br />\n<br />\n大個少少之後，見老豆成日睏廳都唔會入房同老母睏，開始覺得唔正常，但係都無諗太多，可能其實根本係我唔願諗<br />\n<br />\n到近排，老母已經成日唔返屋企，長期寄宿喺一個朋友道，剩係間唔中先會返嚟煮飯執屋，重會探我口風，問我如果同老豆離婚會唔會怨佢，我好亂，唔知點答佢<br />\n<br />\n我重記得佢同我講過，好耐之前佢已經唔想同老豆一齊，只不過係唔想我成長嘅時間無一個完整嘅家庭先一路忍受。但係，而家我已經大個仔，就算無咗佢哋都一樣可以生活到。同埋，佢唔係唔理我，只係唔會再同老豆住，重問我想同佢住定同老豆住。我知道佢同老豆一齊唔開心，但係我亦都唔想頭家散，所以內心好矛盾<br />\n<br />\n直到最近我生日，我哋食咗餐飯。雖然佢哋喺我面前表現到同以前一樣，但我都感覺到有啲嘢係唔同咗，個氣氛係有少少冷冰冰，食飯嗰陣我個心一路都覺得哽住哽住，但係我都盡量笑出嚟，唔想佢哋見到我唔開心<br />\n<br />\n食完飯，老母一路送到我哋去火車站，跟住先走。我望一望老豆，佢竟然有啲眼濕濕，嗰下我真係忍唔住，即刻擰歪面抹一抹啲眼淚。呢個時候，老豆望一望對面月台，說：「我買幾個橘子去。你就在此地，不要走動。」我看那邊月台的柵欄外有幾個賣東西的等著顧客。走到那邊月台，須穿過鐵道，須跳下去又爬上去。父親是一個胖子，走過去自然要費事些。我本來要去的，他不肯，只好讓他去。可是，沒走到一半，幾個穿著短袖襯衫的職員便已經一把拉住他，合力將他抬了回來。父親不從，仍掙扎嚷着要買橘子。很快警察也來了，說父親犯了法規，要關他進牢。<br />\n<br />\n我而家好後悔，如果我話屋企有橙，老豆係咪就唔會畀人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2387e49fa8c5e3707dd2e6f5850a9a671a98956a","tid":315129,"uid":116275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:42:48.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"c8c9918995eb09a4188fb1c85d118375a0b3154e","tid":315129,"uid":14862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:43:10.000Z","msg":"背影"},{"pid":"4161fc7577d16ff8325477266a38e462d2d9b105","tid":315129,"uid":57624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T18:59:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 我喊咗"},{"pid":"94d506313752a842ac213b8542b7d8b9b32370f4","tid":315129,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:04:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"a173d230005f8359d70b995416de4cfc6e6e4477","tid":315129,"uid":92549,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>背影</blockquote><br />\n見到橘子覺得唔對路 但切入幾好<br />\n睇多兩句就好明顯copy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a04ba4d692722ee56a0651804ae76a56578906","tid":315129,"uid":37153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:08:20.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母"},{"pid":"204949c91148c7202f2ec7470f00bd6753f5556e","tid":315129,"uid":7966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:33:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421c22b76115c96692adaac3b8713e444a8dec4a","tid":315129,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:41:16.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f4d299991206a463d521d883cd4f1aaaea2cdf","tid":315129,"uid":90946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:44:08.000Z","msg":"問世上有幾多愛<br />\n流露無限美事<br />\n<br />\n我哭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d883376bb0d51b7dc0a22102dea6a67d8d1bd59b","tid":315129,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a2ff797aae3ed007bfb4828648a0ac4d1c0851","tid":315129,"uid":43907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:56:01.000Z","msg":"睇睇下口語 變左書面語都覺得奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住又欄杆又火車又爬上爬落<br />\n我屌！"},{"pid":"fc8e34db65d840170f2280ec14084d7fe46284b1","tid":315129,"uid":16543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:57:58.000Z","msg":"本身睇到有d心up<br />\n一睇到橘子我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684877448e4420608708a201ec064f61eb84588f","tid":315129,"uid":21922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:58:34.000Z","msg":"唉屌你咩 等我前面仲認真睇諗住安慰你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40aa5e5fa078e869ddea92d124d5bbf7bbe71794","tid":315129,"uid":15481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉屌你咩 等我前面仲認真睇諗住安慰你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9173f03a48d3dede467c2a071237bf6b7470f03","tid":315129,"uid":54478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唉屌你咩 等我前面仲認真睇諗住安慰你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55266120a48b2b2cf1e68d5a7d67584899716b8","tid":315129,"uid":39253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:08:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"46f6fa346ddea2c4dcb32e627726948571de83b8","tid":315129,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T00:39:31.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴打嘅關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今朝我食晒啲橙之後<br />\n心情已經平伏咗好多"},{"pid":"5aba45b013a2c06b39cdef5947a0e6e8915a8566","tid":315129,"uid":66129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T00:46:04.000Z","msg":"之前唔知邊度睇過類似<br />\n個老豆買完橘子返黎比火車撞死咗<br />\n作者話 我啲橘子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f049bba1122dd2aba04f64683dbbcea4578b541","tid":315129,"uid":73859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T01:07:35.000Z","msg":"係咪朱自清嘅背影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616dc447f9ab502b5a989d815f9b4d62a76d3cdb","tid":315129,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲等我認真睇"},{"pid":"d9435074bd4867333d2091263a3682b33a9538d5","tid":315129,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb91684d48be50038582f955d8b47ef2644b561","tid":315129,"uid":19967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"屌 前半段同我差唔多 不過爸媽角色調轉<br />\n後半我屌你呀 背影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47191e060ad40cf1a9126b05d8483ba76c1657b","tid":315129,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:52:26.000Z","msg":"今日老豆開庭，所以我好早就起咗身。本來好緊張，但係今朝見到咁多位巴打為我老豆擔心，我即刻覺得好溫暖，原本失去嘅家庭呢一刻竟然好似再次擁有返，真係好多謝各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日開完庭之後，我先知點解老豆咁執着要去買橘子，原來同當年佢同老母相識有關&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n後生嗰陣，老豆屋企原來係開水果檔，而佢又係屋企入面嘅男丁，所以要幫手托貨運貨。有一次，佢去火車站攞貨嘅時候，唔為意撞低咗個女仔，發泡膠箱入面嘅橙重倒晒落個女仔身上面，老豆即刻嚇到孭咗個女仔去醫院。就係咁，老豆就識咗嗰個女仔嘅老母，即係我老母返嚟<br />\n<br />\n可能就係因為咁樣，嗰晚佢先會咁衝動，爬去對面月台買橘子，而家諗返起我呢個做仔嘅竟然剩係呆喺道，咩都無做，我覺得好慚愧"}]}